Ntiaz Adjaz asks, I was
wondering, are you considering

00:32:58.730 --> 00:33:02.600
starring in a film
with Tom Cruise?

00:33:02.600 --> 00:33:04.130
DAVID BECKHAM: I would
love to star in a

00:33:04.130 --> 00:33:04.850
film with Tom Cruise.

00:33:04.850 --> 00:33:06.100
Who wouldn't?

00:33:08.430 --> 00:33:11.190
People have asked me over the
years, especially when I first

00:33:11.190 --> 00:33:15.560
moved to LA, they were like,
he's obviously going over to

00:33:15.560 --> 00:33:17.190
become an actor.

00:33:17.190 --> 00:33:17.930
And I can't act.

00:33:17.930 --> 00:33:18.740
It's as simple as that.

00:33:18.740 --> 00:33:21.110
It's something that
I've never done.

00:33:21.110 --> 00:33:24.190
I've been involved with,
obviously, adverts and

00:33:24.190 --> 00:33:26.010
different--

00:33:26.010 --> 00:33:29.890
I was involved in a couple of
movies that were about soccer.

00:33:29.890 --> 00:33:32.560
But not major parts.

00:33:32.560 --> 00:33:34.230
Not much talking involved.

00:33:34.230 --> 00:33:37.270
So that was great.

00:33:37.270 --> 00:33:39.120
But who knows?

00:33:39.120 --> 00:33:41.770
Something might happen in the
future that someone comes up

00:33:41.770 --> 00:33:45.560
to me and says you know, we want
you to play this person

00:33:45.560 --> 00:33:49.115
and maybe it will happen.

00:33:49.115 --> 00:33:50.600
But I don't think so.

00:33:50.600 --> 00:33:52.410
It's not something that's
an ambition of mine.

00:33:52.410 --> 00:33:54.640
MARVIN CHOW: You heard it here
first. Something might happen

00:33:54.640 --> 00:33:55.480
in the future.

00:33:55.480 --> 00:33:56.470
DAVID BECKHAM: Exactly.

00:33:56.470 --> 00:33:57.440
Never say never.

00:33:57.440 --> 00:33:58.020
MARVIN CHOW: Never say never.

