He wore the number seven for
Manchester United and England,

00:35:34.010 --> 00:35:39.620
and everything that he did I
wanted to do and become and do

00:35:39.620 --> 00:35:42.170
exactly what he was
like as a player.

00:35:42.170 --> 00:35:45.110
And I was lucky because I wore
number seven for Manchester

00:35:45.110 --> 00:35:49.060
United, wore number seven for
England, and captained England

00:35:49.060 --> 00:35:50.260
and Manchester United.

00:35:50.260 --> 00:35:53.280
So I was very lucky
to have done that.

00:35:53.280 --> 00:35:57.650
So he was a role model
that I looked up to.

