00:42:29.550 --> 00:42:33.220
DAVID BECKHAM: I think
taller the better.

00:42:33.220 --> 00:42:36.600
Put it this way, I've
not worn them.

00:42:36.600 --> 00:42:40.570
She said over the years that I
wore her underwear, for some

00:42:40.570 --> 00:42:42.830
unknown reason.

00:42:42.830 --> 00:42:48.610
She said that live on TV, by
the way, which is not true.

00:42:48.610 --> 00:42:51.290
But the shoes are great.

00:42:51.290 --> 00:42:55.280
I love a pair of high
heels on a lady.

00:42:59.730 --> 00:43:01.022
I like them.

00:43:01.022 --> 00:43:02.810
MARVIN CHOW: Another high heel
question on this side or a

00:43:02.810 --> 00:43:04.310
different question?

00:43:04.310 --> 00:43:05.500
AUDIENCE: Hi David.

00:43:05.500 --> 00:43:06.780
I have a question.

00:43:06.780 --> 00:43:12.220
So if you were to pick a team to
beat, let's say, Barcelona,

00:43:12.220 --> 00:43:13.920
so which one do you
want to choose?

00:43:13.920 --> 00:43:18.290
And do you already have some
ideas to beat them?

00:43:18.290 --> 00:43:20.120
DAVID BECKHAM: I think
to come up against a

00:43:20.120 --> 00:43:23.340
Barcelona team is exciting.

00:43:23.340 --> 00:43:27.360
You can never be worried about
playing against a team.

00:43:27.360 --> 00:43:30.910
As great as Barcelona are, as
great as Real Madrid and

00:43:30.910 --> 00:43:34.600
Manchester United are, we're
a team that's growing.

00:43:34.600 --> 00:43:37.660
And we've got some very good
young players in our team.

00:43:37.660 --> 00:43:40.490
And we've been able, like
I said earlier about the

00:43:40.490 --> 00:43:45.450
interest in this league and
our team around the world,

00:43:45.450 --> 00:43:48.060
we've had some of the biggest
players in the biggest teams

00:43:48.060 --> 00:43:51.200
come over and want to play
against us in preseason games.

00:43:51.200 --> 00:43:57.360
So we've come up against AC
Milan, Barcelona, Real Madrid.

00:43:57.360 --> 00:44:01.860
I was going to say Manchester
City but--

00:44:01.860 --> 00:44:06.010
we've come up against some great
teams and it's great to

00:44:06.010 --> 00:44:09.970
have that interest. So you
should never be worried about

00:44:09.970 --> 00:44:12.720
who you're going to
play against.

00:44:12.720 --> 00:44:14.380
MARVIN CHOW: We'll take one
final question over here and

00:44:14.380 --> 00:44:15.500
then I'll--

00:44:15.500 --> 00:44:16.973
AUDIENCE: One more, please?

00:44:19.920 --> 00:44:21.490
AUDIENCE: Thanks for
coming, David.

00:44:21.490 --> 00:44:23.610
I know you've been around
the league.

00:44:23.610 --> 00:44:26.720
You've been around various
different leagues.

00:44:26.720 --> 00:44:28.520
Where would you like to finish
your soccer career at?

00:44:28.520 --> 00:44:30.550
Would you like to go back
to Manchester United?

00:44:30.550 --> 00:44:32.030
Do you want to stay
in America?

00:44:32.030 --> 00:44:33.870
Or, do you want to tackle
a league that

00:44:33.870 --> 00:44:36.050
